            "title": "取证分析",
            "date_published": "2024-03-23T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p><img src=\"https://starofeden-blog.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/202403241029900.png\" alt=\"image-20240324102901818\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://starofeden-blog.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/202403241030974.png\" alt=\"image-20240324103005907\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://starofeden-blog.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/202403241030042.png\" alt=\"image-20240324103036978\"></p>\n",
            "tags": []
        },
        {
            "id": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/08/17/%E4%BB%8E0%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%84misc%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/",
            "url": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/08/17/%E4%BB%8E0%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%84misc%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/",
            "title": "ctfshow misc做题笔记",
            "date_published": "2023-08-16T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"pcap\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#pcap\">#</a> <strong>.pcap</strong></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>追踪 TCP 流</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"图片\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#图片\">#</a> 图片</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>先用 010 看看文件头：<br>\n（若文件头是 pk 则是压缩包）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"binwalk分离文件\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#binwalk分离文件\">#</a> binwalk 分离文件</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">binwalk -e a.jpg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>若 010 查看文件后无头绪，可用 binwalk 分析，这时不用加 - e</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>可能藏在属性里</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"dd分离\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#dd分离\">#</a> dd 分离</h1>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">dd if=1.jpg of=2.jpg skip=48221 bs=1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>if 指定输入文件，of 指定输出文件，skip 指定从输入文件开头跳过 48221 个块后开始复制 (binwalk 第一列内容)，bs 设置每次读写块的大小为 1 字节</p>\n<h2 id=\"foremost\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#foremost\">#</a> foremost</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"压缩包\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#压缩包\">#</a> 压缩包</h1>\n<p><code>docx拖到010是以压缩包的格式来打开，可以对比压缩包头文件是否毁坏</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>编码转换 - cyberchef</li>\n<li>循环解压</li>\n<li>暴力破解</li>\n<li>明文攻击</li>\n<li>伪加密</li>\n<li>base64 加密（开头是 US）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"密码暴力破解\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#密码暴力破解\">#</a> 密码暴力破解</h2>\n<h2 id=\"可能有密文\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#可能有密文\">#</a> 可能有密文</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>所在位置：<br>\n图片属性</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"zip伪加密\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#zip伪加密\">#</a> zip 伪加密</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://starofeden-blog.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/202403240950186.png\" alt=\"image-20240324095058093\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>识别伪加密</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://starofeden-blog.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/202403240958879.png\" alt=\"image-20240324095837812\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>标志位被修改</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>压缩源文件数据区：<br>\n50 4B 03 04：这是头文件标记  （0x04034b50）<br>\n14 00：解压文件所需 pkware 版本<br>\n 00 00：全局方式位标记（判断有无加密）<br>\n08 00：压缩方式<br>\n 5A 7E：最后修改文件时间<br>\n F7 46：最后修改文件日期</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>50 4B 01 02 1F 00 14 00 09 00 改成 50 4B 01 02 1F 00 14 00 00 00<br>\n<em>50 4B 是 PK，直接搜 PK 就行</em></p>\n<h1 id=\"隐写\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#隐写\">#</a> 隐写</h1>\n<h2 id=\"pdf文件-有水印\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#pdf文件-有水印\">#</a> pdf 文件、有水印</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>全选发现能选中水印，复制到记事本能看见一串密文</li>\n<li>可能是摩斯密码：A：.    B:-     空格：/</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">BABA BBB BA BBA ABA AB B AAB ABAA AB B AA BBB BA AAA BBAABB AABA ABAA AB BBA BBBAAA ABBBB BA AAAB ABBBB AAAAA ABBBB BAAA ABAA AAABB BB AAABB AAAAA AAAAA AAAAB BBA AAABB</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"base64隐写\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#base64隐写\">#</a> base64 隐写</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>CTFCrackTools</li>\n<li>可能是伪加密</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"lsb隐写\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#lsb隐写\">#</a> LSB 隐写</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>stegsolve<br>\n 文件用 stegsolve 打开，Analyse，Date Extract，勾选 red blue green3 个 0，模式选 rbg</li>\n<li>kali zsteg<br>\nzsteg 1.png</li>\n<li>若发现 EP 后文件头为 png 则 save bin 为 png 文件</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"社会主义核心价值观加密\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#社会主义核心价值观加密\">#</a> 社会主义核心价值观加密</h1>\n<h1 id=\"wireshark\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#wireshark\">#</a> WireShark</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>过滤 post 请求（登录密码都是 post 提交）</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">http.request.method==&quot;POST&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"功夫再高也怕菜刀pcapng文件分析\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#功夫再高也怕菜刀pcapng文件分析\">#</a> 功夫再高也怕菜刀 ——pcapng 文件分析</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>拿到一个 pcapng 文件，先 binwalk 分离一下<br>\n分离时有压缩包报错了，安装了 sasquatch 之后成功解压</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">binwalk -eM 6666.pcapng --run-as=root</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>分离之后发现一个压缩包，需要密码</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"wireshark分析\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#wireshark分析\">#</a> wireshark 分析</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>输入表达式：</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">http contains &quot;flag&quot; 或者 tcp contains &quot;flag&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>追踪 TCP 流发现有一个 6666.jpg</li>\n<li>分组字节流搜索 6666.jpg，并追踪 TCP 流，找到 jpg 文件的文件头和文件尾并复制到 WinHex</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://starofeden-blog.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/202403231009656.png\" alt=\"d2ef4e90e67e4adcb52ca8aa6d307295\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"winhex\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#winhex\">#</a> Winhex</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>新建一个文件，剪贴板粘贴选择 ASCLL HEX<br>\n 保存为 jpg 文件打开就可以看到压缩包密码了。</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"ext3-mount挂载文件系统\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#ext3-mount挂载文件系统\">#</a> ext3 - mount 挂载文件系统</h1>\n<p>通过题目名字得知提供的文件是一个 linux 文件系统</p>\n<ul>\n<li>搜索 flag, 找到 flag 文件位置</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">strings linux | grep flag</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">.flag.txt.swp</span><br><span class=\"line\">flag.txtt.swx</span><br><span class=\"line\">~root/Desktop/file/O7avZhikgKgbF/flag.txt</span><br><span class=\"line\">.flag.txt.swp</span><br><span class=\"line\">flag.txtt.swx</span><br><span class=\"line\">.flag.txt.swp</span><br><span class=\"line\">flag.txtt.swx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>mount 挂载文件系统</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo mount linux /mnt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>查看 flag 文件</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cat /mnt/O7avZhikgKgbF/flag.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ZmxhZ3tzYWpiY2lienNrampjbmJoc2J2Y2pianN6Y3N6Ymt6an0=</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>base64 解密</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">base64 -d /mnt/O7avZhikgKgbF/flag.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"misc图片-做题记录\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#misc图片-做题记录\">#</a> misc 图片 - 做题记录</h1>\n<h1 id=\"pngdebugger\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#pngdebugger\">#</a> pngdebugger</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>可以来判断图片宽高是否正确</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>使用方法：<br>\n进入 Debug 目录：</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pngdebugger misc12.png</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"改变图片的宽度\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#改变图片的宽度\">#</a> 改变图片的宽度？</h1>\n<h2 id=\"bmp文件\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#bmp文件\">#</a> bmp 文件</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://starofeden-blog.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/202403132137216.png\" alt=\"image-20240313213710084\"></p>\n<p>减去文件头 54 个字节，最后 2 个字节，信息块 675000 个字节<br>\n文件真实像素为 675000 / 3 = 225000<br>\n 除以图片的宽：900 得到高 250<br>\n 修改高为： <code>FA 00 00 00</code>    (是小端序噢)</p>\n<h1 id=\"时间戳\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#时间戳\">#</a> 时间戳</h1>\n<p>提示：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ctfshow&#123;&#125;, UnixTimestamp, DECtoHEX, getflag</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>把时间戳转十进制（秒）再转十六进制・ <code>注意格式</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">874865822 2699237688 2156662200 460377706</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(hex(874865822)[2:]+hex(2699237688)[2:]+hex(2156662245)[2:]+hex(460377706)[2:])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"exif\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#exif\">#</a> exif</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>可以查看到图片的信息</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">exiftool 文件名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>提示在序列号，是一串数字</li>\n<li>考虑十六进制转 ascii 文本</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"略缩图隐写thumbnail隐写\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#略缩图隐写thumbnail隐写\">#</a> 略缩图隐写（thumbnail 隐写）</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>提示 flag 在图片里，猜测有两张图片</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">exiftool -ThumbnailImage -b misc22.jpg &gt; 1.jpg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>另一种方法是 FFD8</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"python\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#python\">#</a> python</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>文件处理<br>\n <code>把黑白图片转换成0和1</code></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> os</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">white = <span class=\"built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"string\">r&quot;C:\\Users\\xxx\\Desktop\\gif\\0.jpg&quot;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&quot;rb&quot;</span>).read()</span><br><span class=\"line\">black = <span class=\"built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"string\">r&quot;C:\\Users\\xxx\\Desktop\\gif\\1.jpg&quot;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&quot;rb&quot;</span>).read()</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">binary_flag = <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"built_in\">range</span>(<span class=\"number\">104</span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">with</span> <span class=\"built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"string\">r&quot;C:\\Users\\xxx\\Desktop\\gif\\%d.jpg&quot;</span>%i,<span class=\"string\">&quot;rb&quot;</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">as</span> f:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> f.read() == white:</span><br><span class=\"line\">            binary_flag += <span class=\"string\">&quot;0&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">else</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">            binary_flag += <span class=\"string\">&quot;1&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(binary_flag)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">flag = <span class=\"string\">&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"built_in\">range</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">len</span>(binary_flag)//<span class=\"number\">8</span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">    flag += <span class=\"built_in\">chr</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">int</span>(binary_flag[i*<span class=\"number\">8</span>:(i+<span class=\"number\">1</span>)*<span class=\"number\">8</span>],<span class=\"number\">2</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(flag)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>1. 使用绝对路径时前面加个 r 防止转义<br>\n 2.with … as f:<br>\n3. 字符串添加字符：+= “0”<br>\n4.int (binary_flag [i*8:(i+1)*8],2): 将字符串解析为 2 进制数字再转换为 10 进制</p>\n</blockquote>\n",
            "tags": []
        }
    ]
}